217
00:37:01,628 --> 00:37:05,327
Izvinite, nazvaću vas kasnije.

218
00:37:23,570 --> 00:37:25,820
Ko si ti?

219
00:37:33,614 --> 00:37:38,264
Reci mi ko si.

220
00:37:39,168 --> 00:37:43,083
Nisi ona koju želim.

221
00:39:16,016 --> 00:39:18,157
