260
00:47:41,658 --> 00:47:45,367
Mislio sam na tebe kako si sama

261
00:47:45,527 --> 00:47:49,071
u onom potkrovlju i pomislio sam

262
00:47:49,231 --> 00:47:52,733
da bi želela ponekad malo društva.

263
00:47:52,893 --> 00:47:58,174
Svima nam je ponekad potrebno
malo druženja. Zar ne?

264
00:48:00,377 --> 00:48:02,745
